      <title>油价回升至近 83 美元，关注中东停火</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-30</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易商权衡中东可能的停火是否有助于缓解该地区的政治紧张局势，油价收复了近两周来的最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-30</guid>
